data.description: Classic Georgian home by SEMO Campus that you won't want to miss seeing. The home is a unique 2 1/2 story brick that backs up to a small park area for great privacy. Eat-in kitchen with breakfast room and pantry, formal dining room, living and family room all on the main floor. Three bedrooms including a spacious master bedroom suite occupy the second floor and a 4th bedroom and full bath is located in the upper half of the second floor! Hardwood flooring, custom trims and ceilings add to the style and charm of this home. Seller's Disclosure available for many maintained improvements over the past few years. This home is located in Cape Girardeau's Historic District.
